results.description: Implant shall be supplied in sealed sterile packaging
Double packaging system — inner and outer pack
Instructions for use shall accompany the implant
Labels shall comply with ISO 14630 and ISO 15223-1
Nominal volume stated on the unit container label
Implant type/model stated on the unit container
Volume also stated on the implant label (not just container)
Surface classification per normative Annex G, Table G.2
Description of the implant fill material
Shelf life / use-by date on packaging
Do not reuse / single use symbol
CE marking with notified body number
Manufacturer name and full registered address
Product name in official EU member state languages
Surface classification category code on label
Patient implant card included with product
